Package: libharfbuzz
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: an OpenType text shaping engine.
 HarfBuzz is an OpenType text shaping engine.
 .
 This package provides the shared libraries libharfbuzz, libharfbuzz-icu,
 and libharfbuzz-gobject.

