Package: libharfbuzz-dev
Section: libdevel
Provides: harfbuzz-dev
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libharfbuzz (= ${binary:Version}), icu-dev, libfreetype-dev,
 glib2-dev, libgraphite2-dev
Description: Development headers and HarfBuzz static libraries
 This package provides static libraries, headers files and pkgconfig
 data required to build applications, libraries or plugins using the
 HarfBuzz API.
